    (h1 : a ∈ A) (h2 : empty (A \ {a})) : A = {a} := by
  ext x
  constructor
  · intro hxA
    by_contra hxa
    exact h2 ⟨x, hxA, hxa⟩
  · intro hxa
    rw [hxa]
    exact h1
```
